- `02-attendance-rules.md` — codes `0–4`, late windows, blank vs zero
- `03-classlist-import.md` — Registrar TSV `.xls` parse
- `04-session-lifecycle.md` — rotating QR, start/end session
- `05-edge-cases.md` — proxy, timing, overrides
