## Product locks (do not reopen without user ask)

- Primary flow: **student scans rotating classroom QR** (not teacher-scan-every-student)
- Auto codes from server time vs session `T0`
- Unopened sessions stay **blank**; opened + no check-in → **`0`**
- Excel remains analytics/gradebook for MVP; app captures + exports
- **No student password accounts in MVP** — Student ID + confirm + QR + one check-in
- Classroom test: **local app + teacher AP** (not required cloud host)
- Check-in UX: **live name display on**; **speak names optional** (off by default)

## Engineering norms

- Prefer small vertical slices that hit Day 1/2 exit criteria
- Pure functions for scoring (`lib/scoring`) with unit tests
- Server time only for check-in timestamps
- No face/biometric features in MVP
- Do not expand to multi-tenant SaaS in this phase

## When stuck

Re-read `07-phases-2day.md` and cut scope before adding infrastructure.
